snippet.title: Lego Chess (PC, 1998)
snippet.description:
Full campaign playthrough of the Lego Chess PC game. This game has pretty amusing cutscenes and videos each time you capture a piece. There are two campaigns: Pirate levels and Knight levels. 

If you enjoyed this video, check out my playlist with other fun and unique chess games: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLaFBkxox5FqagtxqA_BDLSyjf9dVOI96_

Check out our channel for tons of more gaming videos, let me know if there is anything specific you would like to see. https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCot6qooskKhjsHZ0MicSaaA?sub_confirmation=1
